    <section id="curriculum" class="section section-alt">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Curriculum Structure</h2>
            <div class="modules-list">
                
                <div class="module-item">
                    <div class="module-header">
                        <span class="module-title">1. Foundations of Diachronic Linguistics</span>
                        <span class="module-meta">60 Hours</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>Mechanisms of language change, grammaticalization theories, phonetic and semantic changes. Analysis of case studies from Greek and other languages. Introduction to corpus linguistics concepts.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="module-item">
                    <div class="module-header">
                        <span class="module-title">2. Computational Methods & Tools</span>
                        <span class="module-meta">60 Hours</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>Python/R programming for language analysis, using NLTK/spaCy for text processing, regular expressions, and web scraping. Practical application on real language data.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="module-item">
                    <div class="module-header">
                        <span class="module-title">3. Statistical Analysis & Modeling</span>
                        <span class="module-meta">60 Hours</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>Descriptive statistics, hypothesis testing, regression analysis for linguistic phenomena. Time series models in language evolution and data visualization.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="module-item">
                    <div class="module-header">
                        <span class="module-title">4. Applications in Historical Languages</span>
                        <span class="module-meta">60 Hours</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>Digital processing of ancient/medieval texts, OCR for old editions, polytonic Greek handling, TEI/XML encoding, and creation of digital critical editions.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="module-item">
                    <div class="module-header">
                        <span class="module-title">5. Research Lab</span>
                        <span class="module-meta">60 Hours</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>Development of an original research project, creation of an open dataset/tool, writing a scientific paper, and presentation in conference format.</p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

